WEBVTT

01:31.789 --> 01:34.950
[How dare you!?]

01:35.020 --> 01:37.930
[Episode 31]

01:47.680 --> 01:48.539
Your Highness.

01:50.000 --> 01:50.860
Your Highness.

01:52.370 --> 01:53.710
How is His Majesty doing?

01:53.710 --> 01:54.840
After a rough night,

01:55.350 --> 01:57.210
he's in no serious danger for now.

01:57.310 --> 01:58.440
Physician Xiao said

01:59.120 --> 02:00.480
he was overwhelmed with grief,

02:00.480 --> 02:01.840
causing a surge in his blood

02:01.840 --> 02:03.970
and triggering the poison in his body.

02:04.780 --> 02:06.950
He should keep his emotions
under control from now on

02:06.950 --> 02:09.350
and avoid getting overly excited or upset.

02:10.110 --> 02:10.669
I see.

02:15.280 --> 02:16.140
Your Highness.

02:17.310 --> 02:20.310
His Majesty's headaches are
acting up more frequently.

02:20.310 --> 02:22.079
Although he's like an ordinary man
when he is

02:22.079 --> 02:23.280
not having an attack,

02:23.750 --> 02:25.280
with such a toll on his body,

02:25.360 --> 02:25.890
I fear...

02:34.310 --> 02:35.170
Your Highness.

02:57.720 --> 02:59.579
I had a very long dream.

03:03.150 --> 03:04.540
I dreamed of Mr. Bei.

03:05.190 --> 03:06.790
What did he say in your dream?

03:07.320 --> 03:08.650
He didn't say anything.

03:11.960 --> 03:13.240
He just kept smiling.

03:15.310 --> 03:16.690
Perhaps he met Nan,

03:18.200 --> 03:20.930
the only person in this world
who understood him.

03:29.800 --> 03:31.710
Bai showed me a letter just now,

03:33.560 --> 03:35.960
saying the Nameless
gave it to him long ago.

03:37.970 --> 03:39.360
What does the letter say?

03:39.360 --> 03:42.160
It says that when the Nameless
divined the future,

03:42.510 --> 03:43.750
he told Mr. Bei...

03:46.000 --> 03:48.200
if he came down the mountain to help you,

03:48.430 --> 03:49.760
he would perish.

03:50.340 --> 03:51.490
But he came anyway.

03:53.910 --> 03:55.579
So, in a way,

03:57.170 --> 03:58.560
this was his own choice.

04:11.840 --> 04:14.700
I will bury him
beside Empress Ci Zhen's mausoleum.

04:15.710 --> 04:17.700
It is the only thing I can do for him.

04:19.880 --> 04:20.899
That is not all.

04:21.510 --> 04:23.710
Mr. Bei sacrificed his life to save you.

04:24.070 --> 04:25.000
The best way

04:25.920 --> 04:27.450
to repay him is to live well.

04:32.820 --> 04:34.750
But I don't know how long I can live.

04:35.090 --> 04:35.920
One more day,

04:36.510 --> 04:40.000
one more hour, one more minute,
or even one more second will be good.

04:40.000 --> 04:41.530
As long as you don't give up,

04:42.659 --> 04:43.990
I won't give up, either.

05:24.070 --> 05:25.320
Why didn't he come?

05:26.870 --> 05:27.940
I didn't expect

05:28.070 --> 05:29.730
that you'd be the one who came.

05:31.390 --> 05:33.950
I fought you all as a mortal man.

05:34.960 --> 05:36.490
Although I lost,

05:37.920 --> 05:39.650
I have nothing to be ashamed of.

05:40.630 --> 05:42.680
But you leveraged foresight

05:43.740 --> 05:47.800
and used despicable means such as faking
a surrender to the Three Armies.

05:48.110 --> 05:50.510
It won't sound good if word gets out.

06:01.930 --> 06:03.350
Why aren't you speaking?

06:05.180 --> 06:06.630
Trying to provoke me?

06:08.750 --> 06:09.070
No.

06:11.360 --> 06:12.430
I pity you.

06:14.720 --> 06:16.780
I pity that you've come to this point,

06:17.750 --> 06:19.070
yet you still ascribe your fiasco

06:19.070 --> 06:20.220
to some foresight

06:20.830 --> 06:22.250
or some destined fate.

06:24.800 --> 06:26.130
I might as well tell you.

06:26.430 --> 06:28.430
The Central Army did not betray you.

06:28.600 --> 06:29.630
When they went through all the trouble

06:29.630 --> 06:31.360
to capture His Majesty for you,

06:32.310 --> 06:34.640
they didn't know
he was a fake one, either.

06:36.159 --> 06:38.920
I won't believe a single word you say.

06:39.920 --> 06:41.720
You have never believed anyone.

06:42.720 --> 06:45.050
Her Majesty got your birth mother killed,

06:46.240 --> 06:47.840
but you dared not believe it.

06:48.480 --> 06:51.080
His Majesty wanted
to be a close brother to you,

06:52.190 --> 06:53.850
but you refused to believe it.

06:55.310 --> 06:57.470
Xie Yong'er gave you her true heart,

06:58.360 --> 07:01.160
wanting to stand by your side
in romantic harmony,

07:02.160 --> 07:02.760
but you...

07:05.000 --> 07:07.000
You disdained and didn't believe it.

07:07.000 --> 07:09.260
So stop talking about foresight or what.

07:10.420 --> 07:11.640
You already ruined

07:12.560 --> 07:14.360
your only chance of winning

07:14.360 --> 07:15.430
a long time ago.

07:15.750 --> 07:16.290
Shut up!

07:24.120 --> 07:26.040
Were it not for you, you witch,

07:28.630 --> 07:30.510
would I have lost to Xiahou Dan?

07:36.190 --> 07:36.720
Why?

07:39.390 --> 07:41.110
Why did every single one of you

07:42.430 --> 07:43.390
choose him?

07:47.480 --> 07:48.780
One must love others

07:49.830 --> 07:51.490
before being loved in return.

07:57.270 --> 07:58.330
Stop there!

08:01.000 --> 08:02.530
Winner takes all.

08:03.680 --> 08:06.010
History is written by victors, after all.

08:15.240 --> 08:16.390
Xiahou Dan...

08:19.540 --> 08:21.000
The Emperor's throne

08:21.730 --> 08:23.930
has always been built on piles of bones.

08:25.760 --> 08:28.230
You will not escape this fate either.

08:31.070 --> 08:32.080
-Greetings,
-Greetings,

08:32.080 --> 08:33.809
-Your Majesty.
-Your Majesty.

08:34.720 --> 08:36.049
No need for this formality.

08:36.049 --> 08:36.780
You may rise.

08:37.270 --> 08:38.669
Thank you, Your Majesty.

08:40.000 --> 08:41.080
I'm so glad to see you safe,

08:41.080 --> 08:42.000
Your Majesty.

08:42.630 --> 08:43.530
We thought we'd

08:43.789 --> 08:45.750
never get to see you again, Your Majesty.

08:45.750 --> 08:47.240
We've finally weathered the storm

08:47.240 --> 08:48.720
and made it through.

08:49.120 --> 08:49.870
I heard

08:50.510 --> 08:51.840
that in court, you

08:52.480 --> 08:54.680
not only exposed Prince Duan's treason

08:55.150 --> 08:56.880
but also kept yourselves safe.

08:56.910 --> 08:58.840
Your cooperation was immaculate.

08:59.270 --> 09:00.570
All thanks to Yang

09:01.000 --> 09:03.270
and Er... Lord Er.

09:04.030 --> 09:05.030
Thanks to their help.

09:05.030 --> 09:05.550
Otherwise,

09:05.550 --> 09:07.410
I would have died in the main hall.

09:09.480 --> 09:10.280
Your Majesty,

09:10.510 --> 09:11.960
now that the rebels have been purged,

09:11.960 --> 09:13.030
we're here today

09:13.150 --> 09:14.000
to learn

09:14.030 --> 09:15.360
what the next steps are.

09:15.910 --> 09:17.440
Regaining the Three Armies

09:17.630 --> 09:18.830
and returning safely

09:19.720 --> 09:21.580
constituted only the first step.

09:21.960 --> 09:22.960
In court,

09:23.320 --> 09:25.120
there will be a major reshuffle.

09:25.350 --> 09:26.410
When that happens,

09:27.200 --> 09:28.000
your burdens

09:28.670 --> 09:29.600
will be heavier.

09:30.200 --> 09:31.730
Your Majesty, do you intend

09:32.270 --> 09:33.330
to conduct a purge?

09:34.120 --> 09:34.650
Exactly.

09:39.800 --> 09:41.790
But Prince Duan's remnants
have taken root here deeply.

09:41.790 --> 09:42.590
Acting rashly

09:42.990 --> 09:44.390
might cause great panic.

09:44.550 --> 09:47.610
Who said I am only moving
against Prince Duan's clique?

09:48.120 --> 09:49.320
I will also eliminate

09:50.080 --> 09:51.940
the Empress Dowager's remnants.

10:23.030 --> 10:23.830
Your Majesty.

10:24.530 --> 10:26.730
No need for ceremony, Grand Secretary.

10:27.910 --> 10:29.170
Your Majesty, please.

10:39.440 --> 10:40.840
We haven't met in 5 years.

10:41.150 --> 10:44.320
Your Majesty,
you've made quite some progress at chess.

10:45.550 --> 10:46.550
I am not talented,

10:48.180 --> 10:50.180
not even one-tenth as good as Xu Yao.

10:54.340 --> 10:55.230
Lately,

10:56.270 --> 10:57.930
the court has been in turmoil,

10:58.000 --> 11:00.200
with enemies surrounding like wolves.

11:00.750 --> 11:01.600
I

11:02.150 --> 11:03.280
didn't come sooner,

11:04.120 --> 11:06.380
fearing I would reveal the whereabouts.

11:07.360 --> 11:07.870
Also,

11:10.270 --> 11:13.130
I didn't know how to face you,
my respected teacher.

11:13.830 --> 11:15.890
Years ago, Your Majesty, you asked me

11:17.000 --> 11:20.560
why my son wrote such excellent articles,

11:21.600 --> 11:24.460
yet I didn't let him
pass the imperial examination.

11:25.720 --> 11:27.240
It was because,

11:28.030 --> 11:28.610
although

11:29.480 --> 11:31.340
my son was exceptionally gifted,

11:32.600 --> 11:34.200
he was so naive

11:34.630 --> 11:36.690
that he could easily be manipulated.

11:37.630 --> 11:38.480
I thought

11:39.720 --> 11:41.250
he needed more experience.

11:44.390 --> 11:45.450
I didn't expect...

11:48.270 --> 11:49.150
I didn't expect

11:51.550 --> 11:52.790
that he would still be

11:54.550 --> 11:57.150
used by Prince Duan and led astray.

12:03.630 --> 12:04.790
I am ashamed.

12:06.030 --> 12:07.230
You are wrong, Mr. Xu.

12:08.360 --> 12:10.490
If Xu Yao hadn't risked his life to help

12:11.200 --> 12:13.130
reveal Prince Duan's entire plan,

12:14.150 --> 12:14.480
I

12:16.230 --> 12:18.960
might not have made it here alive
to see you today.

12:28.480 --> 12:29.870
Xu Yao achieved his

12:30.600 --> 12:32.860
"one move to secure the nation's peace."

12:38.360 --> 12:42.490
[Xu Yao]

12:42.750 --> 12:44.080
One move

12:45.360 --> 12:47.550
to secure the nation's peace.

12:53.720 --> 12:56.240
My son died a worthy death.

12:58.000 --> 12:58.440
I

13:00.750 --> 13:01.870
have no regrets.

13:03.190 --> 13:06.140
[The Formation of Roaring Eight Immortals]

13:06.460 --> 13:06.900
[Jiuzhou, 10 Days, 11 Winter]

13:11.720 --> 13:12.840
I came here today

13:13.910 --> 13:15.570
also to ask for one more favor.

13:20.550 --> 13:22.280
Please go ahead, Your Majesty.

13:23.240 --> 13:24.170
Today, although

13:24.750 --> 13:26.950
the obvious enemies have been removed,

13:27.420 --> 13:28.540
the court is still

13:29.320 --> 13:30.920
full of remaining remnants.

13:31.650 --> 13:33.650
I want to get rid of them altogether.

13:33.910 --> 13:34.570
Therefore,

13:35.550 --> 13:37.630
I'd like to invite you,
my teacher, to return

13:37.630 --> 13:38.560
and take charge.

13:39.120 --> 13:42.870
But the court has just settled down,
with the people still feeling uneasy.

13:42.870 --> 13:45.450
Overcorrecting now

13:45.670 --> 13:47.870
might make your reputation as a tyrant

13:48.750 --> 13:51.440
hard to get rid of.

14:03.550 --> 14:05.720
I also want to take it slowly.

14:08.030 --> 14:10.230
It's just that after hiding for so long,

14:11.120 --> 14:12.320
I am gravely poisoned

14:15.630 --> 14:17.290
and don't have much time left.

14:23.960 --> 14:24.760
Your Majesty.

14:25.630 --> 14:26.550
Before I die,

14:28.850 --> 14:30.110
I want to clear

14:30.790 --> 14:32.450
all obstacles for the Empress

14:33.250 --> 14:34.740
and hand over a clean court

14:36.720 --> 14:38.030
and a stable Great Xia

14:40.360 --> 14:41.320
to her.

14:49.770 --> 14:51.350
This is the last thing

14:52.500 --> 14:54.540
I can do for my wife as her husband.

14:57.150 --> 14:59.150
Please help fulfill my wish, Mr. Xu.

15:08.480 --> 15:09.000
I

15:10.600 --> 15:12.730
will certainly not fail this mission.

15:15.240 --> 15:16.170
I firmly believe

15:16.790 --> 15:19.150
that you, Your Majesty, are
the true Son of Heaven.

15:19.150 --> 15:21.840
There's no way you could be replaced
by Prince Duan.

15:21.840 --> 15:23.870
During the days
you were away, Your Majesty,

15:23.870 --> 15:24.360
I

15:24.960 --> 15:27.700
gritted my teeth
for the court and the state,

15:27.960 --> 15:29.370
pretending to cooperate

15:29.840 --> 15:31.440
with Prince Duan's faction.

15:32.390 --> 15:35.770
It really took me quite a lot of effort.

15:44.390 --> 15:46.110
Mr. Chen, your words are

15:46.960 --> 15:49.030
truly moving.

15:51.720 --> 15:52.380
How should I

15:53.600 --> 15:54.750
reward you?

15:56.960 --> 15:57.480
I

15:58.000 --> 15:59.130
do not want a reward.

15:59.630 --> 16:01.360
I only seek to serve our Great Xia

16:01.360 --> 16:02.240
devotedly

16:03.030 --> 16:04.230
until my last breath.

16:07.510 --> 16:08.110
Very well.

16:09.750 --> 16:10.360
Then I

16:11.390 --> 16:12.600
will grant your wish.

16:14.270 --> 16:14.790
Guards!

16:15.320 --> 16:15.820
Yes!

16:16.200 --> 16:16.860
Arrest him!

16:18.910 --> 16:19.710
Your Majesty!

16:19.910 --> 16:21.640
What's this for, Your Majesty?

16:21.670 --> 16:22.470
Your Majesty!

16:22.630 --> 16:23.910
Why, Your Majesty?

16:24.030 --> 16:26.520
Chen Danian and his brother Chen Dasui

16:26.840 --> 16:28.240
sold official positions,

16:28.240 --> 16:29.270
accepted bribes,

16:29.320 --> 16:30.550
formed cliques for personal gain,

16:30.550 --> 16:32.750
and disrupted the court's discipline.

16:33.160 --> 16:34.420
For more than a decade,

16:34.870 --> 16:37.440
they've embezzled
over 100,000 taels of silver,

16:37.440 --> 16:39.380
seized 300,000 mu of fields,

16:40.270 --> 16:42.660
placed spies in various ministries,

16:43.000 --> 16:43.840
and even

16:44.080 --> 16:46.940
secretly colluded with spies
from the Qiang State.

16:50.150 --> 16:51.810
These crimes and evidence are

16:51.910 --> 16:53.110
too many to be listed!

16:53.630 --> 16:54.030
Do you

16:55.960 --> 16:56.960
admit your guilt?

16:57.550 --> 16:58.350
Your Majesty!

16:58.550 --> 16:59.350
It's not true.

16:59.670 --> 17:00.480
I am innocent!

17:00.870 --> 17:02.230
I am innocent!

17:02.610 --> 17:04.210
I knew you wouldn't admit it.

17:07.400 --> 17:08.240
Gu Tingzhi.

17:09.510 --> 17:10.520
Yes, Your Majesty.

17:10.520 --> 17:11.619
Wei Hongyu.

17:12.440 --> 17:13.500
Yes, Your Majesty.

17:13.589 --> 17:14.839
Wu Jiadong.

17:15.200 --> 17:16.400
Yes, Your Majesty.

17:16.510 --> 17:17.700
Wang Ji'an.

17:18.109 --> 17:18.880
Yes, Your Majesty.

17:18.880 --> 17:19.680
Zhao Zili.

17:20.230 --> 17:21.290
Yes, Your Majesty.

17:21.640 --> 17:23.339
Xiao Dingfeng.

17:24.160 --> 17:25.220
Yes, Your Majesty.

17:32.010 --> 17:34.940
Since Mr. Chen
wishes to serve until his last breath,

17:34.950 --> 17:35.750
you,

17:36.950 --> 17:38.810
as his followers,

17:40.830 --> 17:42.560
shall share his wish together!

17:42.590 --> 17:43.390
Your Majesty!

17:43.990 --> 17:45.030
Your Majesty!

17:45.270 --> 17:46.070
Your Majesty.

17:46.640 --> 17:47.440
Your Majesty.

17:47.440 --> 17:48.240
Your Majesty!

17:48.400 --> 17:51.200
You're killing the hounds
once the hare is caught!

17:51.920 --> 17:53.920
If you kill us, your loyal subjects,

17:54.000 --> 17:55.310
who will be left in the court

17:55.310 --> 17:58.590
to serve you, Your Majesty?

17:58.960 --> 17:59.760
About that...

17:59.830 --> 18:00.680
Your Majesty!

18:00.680 --> 18:02.160
It's not your concern.

18:03.110 --> 18:04.160
Your Majesty!

18:04.960 --> 18:05.980
Your Majesty!

18:06.680 --> 18:07.280
Eunuch An.

18:10.920 --> 18:11.690
Summon

18:11.960 --> 18:15.140
Senior Minister Xu to the hall.

18:16.200 --> 18:18.860
Compared to what concerns
Lord Li and Lord Yang,

18:18.920 --> 18:20.190
I am more worried that,

18:20.440 --> 18:22.640
since these two factions are
both made up of veteran officials,

18:22.640 --> 18:24.000
if we uproot them all at once,

18:24.000 --> 18:25.380
we young officials

18:25.680 --> 18:27.090
may struggle to hold the court together.

18:27.090 --> 18:27.640
Exactly.

18:31.530 --> 18:33.250
It is time to invite him back

18:34.040 --> 18:35.200
to take charge.

18:56.270 --> 18:56.900
I am

18:57.610 --> 18:58.780
Xu Huaian.

18:59.070 --> 19:00.710
Greetings, Your Majesty.

19:01.310 --> 19:02.220
Wish you well,

19:02.920 --> 19:03.720
Your Majesty.

19:17.520 --> 19:19.890
[The city fortifications
must be repaired immediately.]

19:34.990 --> 19:37.260
[Xiadu]

19:42.510 --> 19:44.570
The Three Armies rebelled this time,

19:44.680 --> 19:46.960
fighting prefectural garrisons
all the way.

19:46.960 --> 19:49.160
Although we tried our best
to minimize casualties,

19:49.160 --> 19:51.030
many cities were still damaged.

19:51.880 --> 19:52.740
I was thinking,

19:53.550 --> 19:55.150
while we're repairing them,

19:55.400 --> 19:57.720
why not sort out
the transportation infrastructure?

19:57.720 --> 19:58.310
Maybe

19:59.550 --> 20:00.590
we can really get Xie Yong'er's

20:00.590 --> 20:03.650
takeout and express delivery business
up and running.

20:09.070 --> 20:09.550
She...

20:12.110 --> 20:13.310
She is my best friend.

20:17.880 --> 20:19.010
Come and take a look.

20:19.750 --> 20:21.280
See where your hometown is.

20:38.930 --> 20:40.730
My hometown isn't here, either.

20:42.830 --> 20:43.430
It's okay.

20:44.510 --> 20:45.170
From now on,

20:46.070 --> 20:46.670
this place

20:47.440 --> 20:48.640
will be our hometown.

20:51.930 --> 20:53.400
Why are you still so thin?

20:55.000 --> 20:56.270
I'll tell the kitchen

20:56.550 --> 20:58.130
to make you two extra dishes every day.

20:58.130 --> 21:00.020
You're still growing.

21:00.050 --> 21:01.180
You need to eat well.

21:01.830 --> 21:02.240
Got it?

21:07.750 --> 21:08.440
Your Highness,

21:08.440 --> 21:10.040
Physician Xiao has arrived.

21:13.550 --> 21:14.410
Your Highness.

21:14.440 --> 21:15.370
Physician Xiao.

21:15.680 --> 21:16.540
Prince Duan...

21:17.960 --> 21:19.960
Xiahou Bo survived the amputation,

21:20.440 --> 21:22.160
but he still needs to break the fever
and wake up

21:22.160 --> 21:23.620
before he's out of danger.

21:26.750 --> 21:28.410
He really is indestructible.

21:29.480 --> 21:30.080
By the way,

21:30.830 --> 21:32.880
about the "poison against poison" method
we discussed,

21:32.880 --> 21:34.410
have you made any progress?

21:34.550 --> 21:37.110
Regarding the two rare Qiang State poisons
in His Majesty's body,

21:37.110 --> 21:38.240
I have found the remnant

21:38.240 --> 21:39.900
of the ancient prescription,

21:40.000 --> 21:41.200
but it is incomplete.

21:41.680 --> 21:43.030
There are several ingredients

21:43.030 --> 21:44.480
with extremely strange names.

21:44.480 --> 21:46.080
As for what they actually are

21:46.310 --> 21:48.000
or whether they exist in the Great Xia,

21:48.000 --> 21:49.330
I have no way of knowing.

21:52.260 --> 21:53.120
Your Highness,

21:53.640 --> 21:56.840
could you send someone
to the Qiang State to investigate?

21:58.440 --> 21:59.450
A round trip

22:00.480 --> 22:02.080
would take at least 3 months.

22:02.440 --> 22:04.900
I'm afraid His Majesty
can't wait that long.

22:05.720 --> 22:06.440
Physician Xiao,

22:06.440 --> 22:08.440
can you deduce
the effects of the ingredients

22:08.440 --> 22:10.570
and find substitutes in the Great Xia?

22:10.790 --> 22:11.850
Given enough time,

22:11.960 --> 22:12.760
perhaps I can.

22:13.590 --> 22:14.790
"Given enough time"?

22:15.680 --> 22:16.610
At least 3 years.

22:20.440 --> 22:22.640
I will send a message to Tu'er right now.

22:23.310 --> 22:24.710
Let's hope for a miracle.

22:34.200 --> 22:35.060
Your Highness,

22:36.400 --> 22:37.860
regarding Consort Xie...

22:39.200 --> 22:41.400
Did she leave the palace successfully?

22:46.750 --> 22:48.210
After she left the palace,

22:49.720 --> 22:50.650
we lost contact.

22:54.740 --> 22:55.730
Before she left,

22:57.920 --> 22:58.590
she said

23:01.240 --> 23:02.300
she was going home.

23:06.920 --> 23:07.650
That is good.

23:08.070 --> 23:08.800
That is good.

23:12.750 --> 23:14.710
If it is convenient, Your Highness,

23:14.710 --> 23:16.400
please tell Consort Xie

23:18.310 --> 23:19.970
that I have been looking after

23:21.310 --> 23:23.170
the two angelica plants she left.

23:24.670 --> 23:25.870
Tell her not to worry.

23:31.790 --> 23:32.990
I shall take my leave.

23:33.720 --> 23:34.180
Hold on.

23:40.110 --> 23:41.440
Before Yong'er set off,

23:42.560 --> 23:43.960
she left a letter for you.

23:48.920 --> 23:49.600
For me?

24:02.880 --> 24:03.960
Tiny Genius.

24:05.510 --> 24:07.640
I remember your surprised expression

24:07.790 --> 24:09.480
when I called you this for the first time.

24:09.480 --> 24:11.080
It feels like a lifetime ago.

24:11.590 --> 24:12.480
May I have

24:12.830 --> 24:14.070
your name, Imperial Physician?

24:14.070 --> 24:15.550
My name is Xiao Tiancai.

24:16.550 --> 24:17.640
Tiny Genius?

24:18.340 --> 24:20.550
You didn't understand
what I meant back then.

24:20.550 --> 24:21.550
I also didn't know

24:21.880 --> 24:23.270
that you would be the first person

24:23.270 --> 24:26.000
in this palace
who would truly help and accept me.

24:27.480 --> 24:29.940
In the countless times
I brushed with death,

24:30.530 --> 24:32.460
it was you who fought to get me back.

24:33.720 --> 24:35.250
Hope I still have the chance

24:35.510 --> 24:37.970
to express the gratitude
I owe you in person.

24:39.900 --> 24:41.190
When the dust settles,

24:41.400 --> 24:42.680
if I hear about your visit,

24:42.680 --> 24:44.550
I will definitely restore the old bond

24:44.550 --> 24:45.880
and resume our romance.

24:46.310 --> 24:47.110
From Yong'er.

24:57.030 --> 24:58.490
Thank you, Your Highness.

25:00.640 --> 25:01.840
I shall take my leave.

25:10.670 --> 25:11.240
Yong'er.

25:12.850 --> 25:15.110
Just let him think you're out of contact,

25:15.640 --> 25:16.840
wandering the world.

25:19.590 --> 25:21.850
Leave him with a glimmer of hope forever.

26:22.270 --> 26:23.070
What's wrong?

26:24.510 --> 26:25.910
Did you have a nightmare?

26:27.480 --> 26:28.350
Do you remember

26:29.050 --> 26:30.270
when we first met,

26:30.640 --> 26:31.110
I said

26:32.060 --> 26:34.110
the tyrant in "Devil's Favorite Concubine"

26:34.110 --> 26:36.770
died in an assassination
at the end of the story?

26:37.600 --> 26:39.330
I know who the assassin was now.

26:39.550 --> 26:40.150
Who was it?

26:41.000 --> 26:42.330
The original Yu Wanyin

26:42.680 --> 26:44.340
tried to win Prince Duan back,

26:44.350 --> 26:45.150
so she ended up

26:46.160 --> 26:49.020
assassinating the Emperor
with a poisoned dagger.

26:49.630 --> 26:50.190
It was me.

26:51.090 --> 26:51.890
I killed you.

26:58.830 --> 26:59.400
Wanyin.

27:01.790 --> 27:03.990
That was the plot of the original novel.

27:05.960 --> 27:07.090
Xie Yong'er is dead.

27:08.440 --> 27:09.970
Xiahou Bo is crippled, too.

27:10.070 --> 27:11.600
We've nipped

27:12.240 --> 27:13.920
all the disasters in the bud.

27:15.160 --> 27:16.490
We've changed our fate.

27:16.880 --> 27:18.920
But the Nameless's letter emphasized

27:18.920 --> 27:20.790
that when two stars meet,
one is destined to fall.

27:20.790 --> 27:21.590
What he said is

27:22.000 --> 27:23.480
just some meaningless crap.

27:23.480 --> 27:24.720
How could it be crap?

27:25.310 --> 27:26.820
He predicted our arrival

27:26.920 --> 27:28.180
and Mr. Bei's death.

27:28.240 --> 27:29.700
He predicted everything.

27:30.920 --> 27:31.580
Ignore him.

27:32.200 --> 27:33.460
He's just a charlatan.

27:34.350 --> 27:34.850
Look.

27:35.270 --> 27:36.920
What about the five stars align

27:36.920 --> 27:38.120
he mentioned before?

27:40.110 --> 27:41.310
Didn't we get over it?

27:43.320 --> 27:43.830
Don't overthink it.

27:43.830 --> 27:44.960
Five stars align...

27:47.240 --> 27:48.370
Where are you going?

27:49.410 --> 27:50.610
At least put on a coat.

27:58.550 --> 28:00.110
The last time I saw them,

28:01.960 --> 28:03.560
their tails were still bent.

28:06.000 --> 28:06.890
I thought

28:06.980 --> 28:08.200
this ordeal was over.

28:08.920 --> 28:09.780
But it turns out

28:12.920 --> 28:14.160
that it's yet to come.

28:25.380 --> 28:29.070
[Half a month later]

28:39.640 --> 28:40.720
Why are all these officials

28:40.720 --> 28:42.500
coming to meet Her Highness lately?

28:42.500 --> 28:43.920
His Majesty is critically ill.

28:43.920 --> 28:45.610
There must be someone
to handle state affairs.

28:45.610 --> 28:46.920
And the medicine is also

28:46.920 --> 28:48.790
sent to the Yongyan Hall jar after jar.

28:48.790 --> 28:50.350
Her Highness supervises
the brewing herself.

28:50.350 --> 28:52.150
She didn't even have time to eat.

28:53.240 --> 28:55.360
If anything happens to His Majesty,

28:55.790 --> 28:56.460
the palace

28:56.750 --> 28:58.350
can't withstand any more chaos.

28:58.350 --> 28:59.720
Don't say that recklessly!

28:59.720 --> 29:00.650
Get back to work.

29:04.270 --> 29:05.130
Your Highness.

29:06.070 --> 29:07.440
About returning fields to the people,

29:07.440 --> 29:09.240
there is still some dispute in the court.

29:09.240 --> 29:09.830
Should we

29:10.110 --> 29:11.720
delay it for a while?

29:13.030 --> 29:13.490
No need.

29:14.400 --> 29:16.200
Proceed as previously planned.

29:16.720 --> 29:17.980
Ask whoever opposes it

29:18.160 --> 29:19.720
go home and reflect on themselves.

29:19.720 --> 29:20.450
Understood.

29:21.240 --> 29:22.100
Your Highness,

29:22.550 --> 29:23.880
I am already working on reopening

29:23.880 --> 29:25.410
the special imperial exam.

29:26.160 --> 29:27.020
But currently,

29:27.110 --> 29:28.680
we are short of personnel in the court.

29:28.680 --> 29:29.340
Therefore,

29:29.720 --> 29:32.430
Senior Minister Xu has drafted
a list of candidates.

29:32.430 --> 29:35.630
He asked me to present it
to you for review, Your Highness.

29:40.200 --> 29:41.240
Qiu Guangzhi.

29:42.270 --> 29:43.200
Song Yubin.

29:44.270 --> 29:45.000
Luo Shu.

29:46.590 --> 29:48.000
I have read their essays.

29:48.750 --> 29:50.480
Please tell Senior Minister Xu

29:50.480 --> 29:51.830
to appoint them exceptionally.

29:51.830 --> 29:52.560
Understood.

29:57.960 --> 29:58.680
Lord Er,

29:59.550 --> 30:01.280
do you have anything to report?

30:01.830 --> 30:03.680
She's about to resign
and live in seclusion.

30:03.680 --> 30:05.410
What else would she have to say?

30:07.000 --> 30:08.060
You are resigning?

30:11.670 --> 30:12.560
Your Highness,

30:13.240 --> 30:14.500
I am a woman.

30:14.720 --> 30:17.180
Although it's only
between a few of us for now,

30:17.180 --> 30:18.640
it's still improper for me

30:19.200 --> 30:20.110
to serve in the court.

30:20.110 --> 30:21.170
How is it improper?

30:21.830 --> 30:24.160
Wasting a talent
who can benefit the people is

30:24.160 --> 30:25.490
what's truly improper.

30:25.750 --> 30:26.280
Exactly.

30:26.880 --> 30:28.680
Besides, with His Majesty
and Her Highness here,

30:28.680 --> 30:30.880
no one in the court would dare to gossip.

30:32.110 --> 30:33.970
Thank you both for your kindness.

30:34.310 --> 30:36.110
But I've made up my mind to leave.

30:37.480 --> 30:40.080
I hope you can
grant my request, Your Highness.

30:50.270 --> 30:50.790
Lord Er,

30:51.740 --> 30:53.470
could you wait a little longer?

30:53.680 --> 30:55.160
The court is understaffed right now,

30:55.160 --> 30:56.590
and His Majesty is critically ill.

30:56.590 --> 30:58.720
Why don't we give ourselves some time,

30:59.420 --> 31:01.280
wait until His Majesty recovers,

31:01.680 --> 31:03.080
and then make a decision?

31:26.550 --> 31:27.410
Your Highness.

31:29.030 --> 31:29.960
Physician Xiao,

31:30.160 --> 31:31.360
where is General Lin?

31:31.440 --> 31:33.590
General Lin went out of the city
to look for herbs.

31:33.590 --> 31:34.820
He said the Nameless's divination

31:34.820 --> 31:35.680
can't be wrong.

31:36.110 --> 31:37.750
Since the divination says
he can save His Majesty,

31:37.750 --> 31:39.410
then he certainly can make it.

31:39.440 --> 31:40.640
How is His Majesty...

31:41.070 --> 31:41.980
How is he doing?

31:42.350 --> 31:44.350
He had two more episodes last night.

31:44.400 --> 31:46.530
He took the medicine as you instructed

31:46.750 --> 31:48.550
and is currently in a deep sleep.

31:49.900 --> 31:52.310
Why is his condition
deteriorating so fast?

31:52.310 --> 31:54.200
He was able to attend court
just a couple of days ago.

31:54.200 --> 31:56.960
His Majesty's condition is
somewhat similar to Cen Jintian's.

31:56.960 --> 31:58.690
Now that everything is settled

31:59.270 --> 32:01.000
and all obstacles are removed,

32:01.400 --> 32:03.200
the will
that was holding His Majesty up is

32:03.200 --> 32:03.790
gone.

32:06.720 --> 32:07.920
How long does he have?

32:07.920 --> 32:09.250
This poison in the blood

32:09.720 --> 32:11.850
has affected His Majesty's mobility.

32:12.790 --> 32:13.440
He may be

32:14.110 --> 32:16.370
unable to move in the next couple of days.

32:16.440 --> 32:17.830
Delirium will follow.

32:19.030 --> 32:19.640
At most...

32:23.200 --> 32:25.000
At most, he has 10 to 15 days left.

32:27.880 --> 32:28.740
Your Highness.

32:30.200 --> 32:31.000
In that case,

32:32.780 --> 32:33.710
Physician Xiao,

32:34.550 --> 32:36.080
please increase his dosage

32:36.720 --> 32:38.920
and keep him asleep as much as possible.

32:38.920 --> 32:40.120
Don't let him suffer.

32:41.070 --> 32:41.800
Understood.

32:47.310 --> 32:49.570
Won't you go in to see him, Your Highness?

32:49.720 --> 32:52.120
He said he wants me
to remember him as he was,

32:53.060 --> 32:54.120
not as he is now.

32:56.880 --> 32:57.940
I respect his wish.

33:23.240 --> 33:24.510
When two stars meet,

33:25.110 --> 33:26.440
one is destined to fall.

33:27.380 --> 33:28.770
Five stars align,

33:34.470 --> 33:36.600
amidst despair, great fortune rises.

33:39.400 --> 33:40.550
For this world,

33:41.400 --> 33:42.820
losing a mad king

33:43.510 --> 33:44.640
to gain an empress is

33:46.400 --> 33:47.330
quite a bargain.

33:48.390 --> 33:49.610
Don't talk nonsense.

33:51.000 --> 33:54.270
Only surviving counts
as "amidst despair, great fortune rises."

33:54.270 --> 33:54.880
Wanyin.

33:57.550 --> 33:59.080
Everyone dies eventually.

34:00.440 --> 34:01.900
Instead of losing my mind,

34:03.110 --> 34:05.390
wailing for days before I pass away,

34:07.960 --> 34:09.560
I'd rather die a quick death.

34:10.280 --> 34:11.210
What do you mean?

34:13.360 --> 34:15.489
You want me to kill you with my own hands

34:16.230 --> 34:17.760
like in the original novel?

34:20.699 --> 34:21.679
Of course not.

34:24.070 --> 34:24.760
I just don't want

34:24.760 --> 34:26.219
to leave you my worst side.

34:26.920 --> 34:28.920
So you knew it all along, didn't you?

34:29.150 --> 34:31.250
You knew only one of us could survive.

34:32.969 --> 34:34.949
How could you be so cruel to me?

34:39.550 --> 34:41.750
You told me you wouldn't leave me alone.

34:42.760 --> 34:43.760
You lied to me.

34:45.699 --> 34:46.679
If I'd known,

34:47.699 --> 34:48.690
♪ Tell me ♪

34:48.760 --> 34:51.030
you should have kicked me
out of the palace in the first place,

34:49.350 --> 34:52.810
♪ Why so many laments echo in the wind ♪

34:51.670 --> 34:53.670
or I should have come after you died.

34:54.420 --> 34:55.570
♪ Walk past me ♪

34:55.870 --> 34:59.570
♪ Like an aloof passerby ♪

34:56.710 --> 34:58.390
I wish I'd never met you.

34:58.670 --> 35:00.800
I wish I'd never eaten hot pot with you.

35:00.800 --> 35:02.280
I wish I'd never fallen for your tricks.

35:00.960 --> 35:03.500
♪ Don't watch me as the rain falls ♪

35:02.280 --> 35:04.210
I wish I'd never read your letters.

35:04.270 --> 35:07.000
♪ Love burns too hot as it passes ♪

35:07.820 --> 35:13.520
♪ Even a lifetime of war
cannot be extinguished ♪

35:14.630 --> 35:15.760
♪ Blame me ♪

35:16.420 --> 35:19.910
♪ For the frailty of fate ♪

35:21.480 --> 35:22.760
♪ Hide me ♪

35:23.170 --> 35:27.080
♪ With light snow or thick ink ♪

35:23.880 --> 35:25.080
But fortunately,

35:26.760 --> 35:27.880
our Empress is

35:28.320 --> 35:30.790
♪ We met in the crowd ♪

35:28.750 --> 35:29.950
so magnanimous

35:31.440 --> 35:32.880
that she will repay malice with kindness,

35:31.650 --> 35:34.320
♪ There's no mistake in this life ♪

35:33.880 --> 35:35.190
follow the will of Heaven and the people,

35:35.190 --> 35:38.180
♪ I only regret being clumsy in words ♪

35:36.880 --> 35:38.030
and reign for ages.

35:38.260 --> 35:40.320
♪ And shrinking from speaking it out ♪

35:40.510 --> 35:41.400
No, I don't want it.

35:40.710 --> 35:43.090
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

35:42.030 --> 35:42.760
Without you,

35:43.070 --> 35:44.030
I can't go on.

35:43.150 --> 35:45.020
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

35:45.050 --> 35:47.520
♪ I never yielded ♪

35:45.440 --> 35:46.190
You can do it

35:47.800 --> 35:49.300
♪ But why ♪

35:47.880 --> 35:48.760
Bai told me.

35:49.570 --> 35:54.060
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

35:51.110 --> 35:53.020
Before I came back,

35:53.040 --> 35:53.850
you could

35:54.480 --> 35:56.850
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

35:54.550 --> 35:55.840
hold your own, right?

35:56.900 --> 35:58.700
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

35:58.770 --> 36:01.080
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

35:58.840 --> 36:00.840
You'll do even better in the future.

36:01.440 --> 36:03.320
♪ The first time I met you ♪

36:01.960 --> 36:02.560
Don't cry.

36:03.670 --> 36:12.620
♪ It felt like something suddenly
lit up my soul ♪

36:05.090 --> 36:06.190
I apologize to you.

36:07.510 --> 36:08.030
Okay?

36:11.710 --> 36:13.910
If reincarnation exists in this world,

36:16.110 --> 36:16.800
I will repay

36:19.400 --> 36:21.060
what I owe you in the next life.

36:22.150 --> 36:23.610
I don't want the next life.

36:24.150 --> 36:25.510
I want this life.

36:26.550 --> 36:27.680
♪ Blame me ♪

36:27.710 --> 36:28.810
I want you to stay

36:28.320 --> 36:31.820
♪ For the frailty of fate ♪

36:29.510 --> 36:30.550
by my side.

36:33.440 --> 36:34.500
♪ Hide me ♪

36:35.180 --> 36:38.980
♪ With light snow or thick ink ♪

36:36.000 --> 36:37.730
I want to stay more than anyone.

36:40.310 --> 36:42.760
♪ We met in the crowd ♪

36:43.680 --> 36:46.240
♪ There's no mistake in this life ♪

36:47.240 --> 36:50.220
♪ I only regret being clumsy in words ♪

36:47.380 --> 36:48.920
But I have no choice.

36:50.240 --> 36:52.340
♪ And shrinking from speaking it out ♪

36:52.810 --> 36:55.230
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

36:55.280 --> 36:57.040
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

36:55.880 --> 36:56.480
Wanyin...

36:57.070 --> 36:59.590
♪ I never yielded ♪

36:59.230 --> 37:00.270
If I die,

36:59.900 --> 37:01.420
♪ But why ♪

37:01.630 --> 37:06.120
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

37:02.190 --> 37:04.590
I can return to the world
outside the novel.

37:06.190 --> 37:07.580
I will definitely go find you then.

37:06.530 --> 37:08.890
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

37:08.930 --> 37:10.780
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

37:10.800 --> 37:11.840
If I can't go back...

37:10.830 --> 37:13.150
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

37:13.620 --> 37:15.320
♪ The first time I met you ♪

37:15.910 --> 37:18.830
♪ There was once light ♪

37:17.230 --> 37:18.970
Please remember me as I am now.

37:19.410 --> 37:27.790
♪ In my soul ♪

37:23.360 --> 37:24.960
Let's say goodbye properly.

37:27.870 --> 37:29.430
I don't want to.

37:33.890 --> 37:36.310
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

37:36.360 --> 37:38.230
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

37:38.250 --> 37:40.720
♪ I never yielded ♪

37:41.010 --> 37:42.480
♪ But why ♪

37:42.800 --> 37:47.400
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

37:47.710 --> 37:50.070
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

37:49.670 --> 37:51.510
If one of us has to die,

37:50.110 --> 37:51.960
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

37:52.010 --> 37:54.330
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

37:53.920 --> 37:55.030
it could be me.

37:54.740 --> 37:56.510
♪ The first time I met you ♪

37:57.040 --> 38:04.930
♪ It felt like something suddenly
lit up my soul ♪

38:00.400 --> 38:01.260
Your Highness,

38:01.880 --> 38:02.940
it's getting late.

38:03.260 --> 38:04.320
Please rest early.

38:23.760 --> 38:24.620
Your Highness.

38:25.510 --> 38:26.000
Twelve?

38:27.030 --> 38:28.090
What's the matter?

38:28.150 --> 38:29.010
Your Highness.

38:29.440 --> 38:30.420
That mute girl

38:30.510 --> 38:33.170
tried to sneak
into the small pharmacy just now.

38:37.630 --> 38:39.030
The small pharmacy was

38:39.440 --> 38:41.240
remodeled specifically to hide

38:41.280 --> 38:42.670
His Majesty's illness.

38:43.280 --> 38:44.540
It's heavily guarded.

38:45.280 --> 38:48.010
There's no way
ordinary maids can get close to it.

38:48.280 --> 38:49.680
What was she doing there?

38:49.710 --> 38:50.550
I do not know.

38:51.110 --> 38:51.980
She is cunning.

38:52.360 --> 38:54.320
She seemed to know
where the other secret guards were

38:54.320 --> 38:55.760
and moved extremely fast.

38:55.760 --> 38:57.760
Only I was newly added to today's shift,

38:57.760 --> 38:59.230
and so was my post.

38:59.400 --> 39:00.600
She did not know that,

39:00.630 --> 39:02.090
so I spotted her movement.

39:02.360 --> 39:03.590
How is it on His Majesty's side?

39:03.590 --> 39:04.800
Don't worry, Your Highness.

39:04.800 --> 39:06.590
The side hall is impregnable right now.

39:06.590 --> 39:07.650
No one can sneak in.

39:08.280 --> 39:09.140
Just to be safe,

39:09.670 --> 39:11.550
tell the side hall to pour out
all the medicine sent

39:11.550 --> 39:12.630
by the small pharmacy today

39:12.630 --> 39:13.880
and brew it over again.

39:13.880 --> 39:14.610
Understood.

39:45.960 --> 39:47.510
I still have a lot to do,

39:47.880 --> 39:48.740
so I'll skip it.

40:01.000 --> 40:02.660
Isn't that what I said before?

40:54.320 --> 40:54.800
Help...

40:55.960 --> 40:56.820
Someone, help.

41:02.000 --> 41:02.770
Flower,

41:03.480 --> 41:03.880
hurry.

41:04.280 --> 41:06.080
Fetch me an imperial physician.

41:06.190 --> 41:07.190
I don't feel well.

41:10.920 --> 41:11.900
It is pointless.

41:12.320 --> 41:13.360
You are poisoned.

41:19.880 --> 41:20.360
You...

41:22.030 --> 41:23.080
You can speak?

41:31.710 --> 41:32.550
That soup.

41:35.120 --> 41:36.250
All day today,

41:37.480 --> 41:39.530
I only ate the soup you brought me.

41:41.190 --> 41:42.520
Take me to the pharmacy.

41:42.920 --> 41:44.180
Once the Emperor dies,

41:44.400 --> 41:45.930
I'll give you the antidote,

41:46.070 --> 41:47.200
and you can survive.

41:49.280 --> 41:50.880
You are from the Qiang State?

41:50.920 --> 41:51.280
Yes.

41:52.840 --> 41:54.500
You entered the palace with me

41:55.150 --> 41:56.550
just to assassinate him?

41:57.110 --> 41:57.910
That is right.

41:59.510 --> 42:01.320
But after you entered the palace,

42:01.320 --> 42:03.050
your clothes were all changed.

42:03.880 --> 42:05.480
Where did you get the poison?

42:07.280 --> 42:07.830
Heaven is

42:09.070 --> 42:10.050
helping me.

42:11.550 --> 42:12.500
What do you mean?

42:13.510 --> 42:15.040
You only have 2 hours left.

42:15.550 --> 42:16.550
If we don't go now,

42:16.840 --> 42:17.960
you will die.

42:22.150 --> 42:23.200
I cannot do it.

42:24.280 --> 42:27.230
All of His Majesty's food
and drink is specifically checked.

42:27.230 --> 42:29.190
Even if I put poison in the medicine,

42:29.190 --> 42:31.150
the imperial physician will find it out.

42:31.150 --> 42:31.960
He trusts you.

42:32.590 --> 42:33.590
He won't check the medicine

42:33.590 --> 42:34.320
you give him.

42:36.030 --> 42:38.150
His Majesty does not have long to live.

42:38.150 --> 42:39.550
Why go to such trouble?

42:40.920 --> 42:41.780
My parents were

42:42.030 --> 42:43.370
the Queen's warriors.

42:43.510 --> 42:45.110
But the Emperor killed them.

42:45.150 --> 42:45.710
So,

42:46.000 --> 42:48.000
I'll take revenge with my own hands.

42:52.510 --> 42:53.370
Your Highness.

42:53.880 --> 42:55.940
What brings you here so late at night?

42:56.110 --> 42:58.510
I'm here
to check on His Majesty's medicine.

42:58.510 --> 42:59.360
It was just finished

42:59.360 --> 43:00.670
and ready to be sent over.

43:00.670 --> 43:01.930
Flower and I are here.

43:02.360 --> 43:03.420
You may go and rest.

43:04.110 --> 43:04.550
Yes.

43:05.360 --> 43:06.480
The rest of you may leave as well.

43:06.480 --> 43:06.760
Yes.

43:06.760 --> 43:07.030
Yes.

43:17.280 --> 43:19.540
It's not too late to change your mind now.

43:21.400 --> 43:21.960
Put this

43:22.400 --> 43:23.460
into the medicine.

43:24.190 --> 43:25.720
Once the Emperor drinks it,

43:25.800 --> 43:26.800
you will survive.

43:45.840 --> 43:46.370
Quickly!

43:47.550 --> 43:48.110
Twelve.

43:51.430 --> 43:52.090
Don't move!

43:52.550 --> 43:53.830
So you knew all along!

43:55.110 --> 43:57.170
I had hoped my suspicions were wrong.

43:57.320 --> 43:58.440
Where is the antidote?

43:58.440 --> 43:59.550
The Qiang State's poison

43:59.550 --> 44:00.210
has no cure.

44:02.880 --> 44:03.740
Your Highness.

44:04.000 --> 44:05.260
Should we use torture?

44:06.920 --> 44:07.660
Forget it.

44:08.220 --> 44:09.150
She isn't lying.

44:10.510 --> 44:11.910
Send this packet of drugs

44:11.920 --> 44:12.920
to Physician Xiao

44:13.000 --> 44:14.210
and see if it helps.

44:14.550 --> 44:14.840
Yes.

44:19.410 --> 44:20.560
Escort me to His Majesty's place.

44:20.560 --> 44:21.560
There are only 2 hours left.

44:21.560 --> 44:22.030
Hurry.
